Love this DVD & it's on frequent rotation in my house! I'm a huge fan and pride myself on my juggalette status.  If you ever want to see a sneak peek about tour life, Faygo, and juggalo culture this one is for you!

Great dvd! A VIP look at I.C.P. ,Twiztid and others on the American Psycho Tour! Buy this dvd and join all the fun! Over two hours of backstage and live footage! Covers all 32 shows in 34 days! Get to know the backstage crew, The fans, Twiztid, ICP, Blaze, Mike E Clark, Hutch, and everyone else they meet on the tour on a whole diffrent level! Even if your not a fan of the music you will enjoy this documentary. No bonus footage or extras on this dvd, but who needs it, the Documentary itself gives you all you need! Pick it up now!
my son absolutely loves this. he really wanted a different one but when he got this one he decided he liked it more
